What is ETL Entities?
-----------------------

Collection of classes used for handling High Water Mark (HWM) and gathering Lineage graph.

Currently implemented:
    * ``IntHWM``
    * ``DateHWM``
    * ``DateTimeHWM``
    * ``FileListHWM``
    * ``Column``
    * ``Table``
    * ``RemoteFolder``
    * ``Process``

.. installation

How to install
---------------

.. code:: bash

    pip install etl-entities

